content: Total operating expenses were 10.3% of net sales in the first quarter of fiscal year 2023, compared with 10.6% of net sales for the same period in fiscal year 20 -- 2022. Selling and marketing expenses were 4.7% of net sales in the first quarter of fiscal year 2023, compared with 5.2% of net sales for the same period in fiscal year 2022. General and administrative expenses were 5.6% of net sales in the first quarter of fiscal year 2023, compared with 5.4% of net sales for the same period of fiscal year 2022.
